Package marvel

Class MainPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • marvel.MainPresenter
  • public class MainPresenter
extends java.lang.Object
    MainPresenter class observes the main view (Main.fxml), triggers Model operations upon user events, and ask corresponding view components to update accordingly via manipulating FXML attributes.
    See Also:
    View, ViewSwitcher
